scene.message:
Trish: Hi! I'm Trish!{nl}
This is the Fountain of{nl}
Recovery!{waitkey}{clearbox}The world runs on give and{nl}
take! For the right price,{nl}
I'll Recover anything!{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Let's see, the going{nl}
rate for healing these days{nl}
is about this much, so for{nl}
everyone...{waitkey}{ret}

Trish: Boo~! You don't have{nl}
any money?! Trish doesn't{nl}
like broke people!{waitkey}{clearbox}Come back after you've saved{nl}
up some money. Bye-bye!{waitkey}{ret}
